Summary: taking pics,outside of birds ect. noticed strange object going across the sky.
divs: Sighting Detailsjust bought a new camara,so i was in the backyard taking a few photos trying out the camara,has a nice 12x zoom,i saw a plane above so i thought i would zoom in on it and get a shot. than i noticed out of the corner of my eye a strange,object to the east(now planes travel all the time in this area so im very aware of there shapes and sound and vaper trails ect)this object made no sound and was traveling at a good rate of speed heading south east in a straight line, it was hard to find the object already zoomed(camara)just caught it in back of trees,and the camara(of course)focused on the tree if i would have got it in frame sooner it would have been better.than object went though clouds and i lost sight of it. now i would not have reported this but 1 month earlyer we were walking dogs at around 8pm and noticed strange lites coming from the south heading in about the same direction it was 4 or 5 lites in a row and made no sound and in a few min. maybe 4 it just disappered.
